{"tid":1883321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雞管局放生]黨友成功撲口罩 容海恩成功接機","createTime":"2020-02-17T00:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T02:16:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d8ec8488ba0bcbc6ae8acab9a20e1345abd091","tid":1883321,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新民黨社區發展主任劉文杰同孔永業，早前聯同兩個助手飛去印尼採購口罩，日前帶咗5萬幾個口罩返香港，新民黨立法會議員容海恩（Eunice）親自接機。之不過，機場仍然實施進出管制，市民照計係唔可以入客運大樓接機。Eunice同Emily講，佢都唔知係咪有放寬，話「喺接機大堂口話入去接機，工作人員就示意我進入」。佢話當時戴住口罩，亦唔使出示身分證明。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n劉文杰同孔永業去咗印尼三日兩夜採購口罩。劉文杰話當地口罩價格上升幅度「好比火箭升空速度」，只差一日半日，口罩價格嘅升幅可以係50%以上；當地有啲老闆娘亦唔畀講價。劉文杰話口罩連同小量個人行李總重超過220公斤，運送時非常困難，好在有紅白藍袋。<br />\n機場仍然實施進出管制<br />\n<br />\nEunice話，之前有朋友喺外地寄口罩返港，但被當地扣起，今次有勞劉文杰等專程買口罩返港，確保口罩安全送到，可盡快發放到地區幫助有需要嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200217/s00002/1581878582331/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e9%bb%a8%e5%8f%8b%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%92%b2%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e5%ae%b9%e6%b5%b7%e6%81%a9%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%8e%a5%e6%a9%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200217%2Fs00002%2F1581878582331%2F%25e3%2580%2590emily%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e5%258f%258b%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258a%259f%25e6%2592%25b2%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%2581%25a9%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258a%259f%25e6%258e%25a5%25e6%25a9%259f&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b41d0875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200217%2Fs00002%2F1581878582331%2F%25e3%2580%2590emily%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e5%258f%258b%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258a%259f%25e6%2592%25b2%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%2581%25a9%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258a%259f%25e6%258e%25a5%25e6%25a9%259f&h=391bd179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200217/s00002/1581878582331/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e9%bb%a8%e5%8f%8b%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%92%b2%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e5%ae%b9%e6%b5%b7%e6%81%a9%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%8e%a5%e6%a9%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200217/s00046/191bbee3a46cb3ca552d5d55d80f7f6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200217%2Fs00046%2F191bbee3a46cb3ca552d5d55d80f7f6e.jpg&h=b39bc3cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f1556bfb0f5f33a6827ce72f6fab78cae188666","tid":1883321,"uid":265839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"知法犯法"},{"pid":"e2ae3d5987cfb074000f12dc87a418c4c574e289","tid":1883321,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:15:07.000Z","msg":"支那水貨狗咁款<br />\n<br />\n非洲佬機場走水貨都識得用晒黑袋啦，邊有咁肉酸架"},{"pid":"65ed2822b65a858899ab436a94ff91f5c5a93439","tid":1883321,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"禁制令WFC"},{"pid":"76bb5edaec883122f1f350fec37056d5c5d33fc8","tid":1883321,"uid":1470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"真心講<br />\n用紅白藍寄倉，比人掉到壓扁哂D盒 分分鐘爆埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印尼連紙箱都冇咩"},{"pid":"0b810f5a3a18b0c33b1840f91f55d34a597a4999","tid":1883321,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"告唔告得機管局"},{"pid":"18be1e74e71b2057cfd82a5f0dbfbecd5068b8c9","tid":1883321,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"平機會Port爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次老母翻黎我都無得接"},{"pid":"444262c88a548e6d74f266e72d211e4f1f2a7713","tid":1883321,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB